"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640879579,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"GhuESibxDLlVgej-946LThuuBg4jgPBZSeR9OQF3tO8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc12187b4887879910c1A41ff21837194EAD132fe\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c2os75OiCYTv4sMxhNv2rry5J_D2lzHM_ARCpKkAIMg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"XTV7BWxHAquWlQZ3g0CbODT5U6BEoFeb8ZiXqxDHK_o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8ZIm-MaqBI3oWkJwTNGLi9mcDCp6P6zhHNv2Bqu779QF6sBvVNa8-bwjbQwkR1qNxbMuQ_h7hyRP5_Bc_Iw49A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1e898c8fc1babf168f7d519ca341a48cef7919f29ffc8bcf95a2a60a6904d851439b970cbb177908416b34422f3cca61cb5c29da7ca1ce4d8228f811943dc0541c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c2os75OiCYTv4sMxhNv2rry5J_D2lzHM_ARCpKkAIMg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"XTV7BWxHAquWlQZ3g0CbODT5U6BEoFeb8ZiXqxDHK_o\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi